data.description: Situated on 2.77 acres of flat, usable land, sits two homes on one expansive lot. The primary residence has recently been renovated in 2021/2022, boasting 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. A newly remodeled kitchen, new flooring, double pane windows, and custom window shutters are complemented with an attached 2-car garage. The second dwelling, known as Unit B, also has 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom and is currently yielding rental income. Located in close proximity to Monterey rd. and Highway 101, this property provides the ideal balance for commuters and accessibility. The property features newly constructed concrete pads designed to accommodate work trucks or oversized vehicles, making it a perfect space for business or hobby-related activities. Additionally, a custom treated wooden fence surrounds the property, presenting a sleek and refined aesthetic. Whether you're envisioning a peaceful retreat, picturesque mountain views, a multi-generational living arrangement, or an income-generating property, this listing has the potential to fulfill your aspirations.
